1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,920
Hey! Mmph!

2
00:00:02,920 --> 00:00:06,510
So warm.
This'll keep me from getting sick.

3
00:00:07,010 --> 00:00:10,550
You're too strong. I can't get away.

4
00:00:14,060 --> 00:00:18,230
Ouch.

5
00:00:21,230 --> 00:00:23,940
(Wait, what's going on?)

6
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:28,190
(I think I remember... we got into a fight over Natsu yesterday.)

7
00:00:28,190 --> 00:00:31,320
(Then there was an accident... and I was pinned under Makoto.)

8
00:00:31,320 --> 00:00:33,350
(Huh? So what's happening now?)

9
00:00:33,350 --> 00:00:34,660
(This is really, really bad.)

10
00:00:34,660 --> 00:00:39,160
(But I think I heard
Makoto and Natsu talking...)

11
00:00:40,420 --> 00:00:44,170
He wasn't jealous of me.
He was jealous of Makoto-kun.

12
00:00:44,170 --> 00:00:46,420
What does that mean?

13
00:00:46,420 --> 00:00:49,050
You idiots... What exactly did you two talk about?

14
00:00:49,050 --> 00:00:52,050
Mmm... Nngh.

15
00:00:53,300 --> 00:00:54,930
Could this be...?

16
00:00:56,470 --> 00:00:57,890
Mmm...

17
00:00:57,890 --> 00:00:59,060
Good morning, Yuki.

18
00:00:59,060 --> 00:01:00,060
Morning.

19
00:01:00,060 --> 00:01:01,940
You were a real handful yesterday.

20
00:01:01,940 --> 00:01:02,980
Sorry.

21
00:01:03,610 --> 00:01:05,480
(That cut on Makoto's ear...)

22
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:06,860
(Don't tell me...)
